1.00	Chikamatsu_monogatari	The Crucified Lovers	The Crucified Lovers Chikamatsu Monogatari, literally, "A Story From Chikamatsu") is a 1954 black-and-white Japanese film directed by Kenji Mizoguchi. It was adapted from Monzaemon Chikamatsu's 17th century play Daikyoji sekireki' ' (大経師昔暦), hence the title.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/88/Chikamatsu_monogatari_poster.jpg/220px-Chikamatsu_monogatari_poster.jpg
